{"tid":953951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入境處交代「閃靈」不獲發簽證原因：冇特殊技能","createTime":"2018-12-24T09:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T14:49:00.000Z","uid":79382,"like":22,"dislike":230,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"20d6cff37084623c61bf425e11886ccd3bc79417","tid":953951,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T09:51:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100375550229/posts/10161314509810230/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100375550229%2Fposts%2F10161314509810230%2F&d=d2yxd3y3fXcjSCKVnkSSFv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=ba210b6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100375550229/posts/10161314509810230/</a><br />\n<br />\nSource: HOCC Facebook <br />\n<br />\n終於收到入境處回覆。佢地俾個原因真係好DA意⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n「Under existing policy, a person seeking to enter into HKSAR for employment should , amongst other things, possess a special skill, knowledge or experience of value and not readily available in the HKSAR」<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n哦，原來只要你無香港境內不存在嘅技能或知識經驗，你都唔洗旨意攞到簽證。咁各位外籍人士由而家開始記得練定隱形啊、分身術啊、時空轉移等等特異功能先好嚟申請工作證喇💁🏿&zwj;♂️。<br />\n<br />\n不過而家只係收到主唱Freddy嘅申請回覆，其他幾位成員嘅申請依然音訊全無。<br />\n<br />\n#笑死街坊系列<br />\n#咁計法應該全港所有工作證都要取消<br />\n#低B政府<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n要幾on9先作到呢個原因 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班撚屌個腦裝屎<br />\n嘥咁多日諗個咁廢嘅解釋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8d5b738e302e26c6b02394b7ee85c68d8a2d9b","tid":953951,"uid":70183,"like":60,"dislike":2,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T09:52:43.000Z","msg":"大sir 放梗假冇人話到事"},{"pid":"d87dc4bab8d6fbd3312a0f28da50d59625e1060e","tid":953951,"uid":41508,"like":167,"dislike":4,"score":163,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T09:54:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3da30c726568c3a33c80184935f04c77b5066e8c","tid":953951,"uid":79382,"like":114,"dislike":1,"score":113,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T09:54:59.000Z","msg":"其實佢都係嚟出